author: britneyspears
content: .@iTunesMusic #BritneyJean is very special to me! It's a diff album than any other album I've recorded throughout my career... #AskBritney

author: britneyspears
content: I typically make albums that are fun pop/dance records & #BritneyJean has a few, but... #AskBritney

author: britneyspears
content: It also has a lot of personal songs. Songs that are very moody and vibe driven. #AskBritney

author: britneyspears
content: .@iTunesMusic Of course! I've recorded a few songs in the past specifically about my boys and they are my daily inspiration. :) #AskBritney

author: britneyspears
content: .@iTunesMusic On this album I mostly drew from personal experience. #BritneyJean was therapeutic... #AskBritney

author: britneyspears
content: I used this album to get out everything I'd bottled up over the last few years... #AskBritney

author: britneyspears
content: I tend to write from experience, but also enjoy fantasizing & writing from imagination. #AskBritney

content: .@iTunesMusic The features may be surprising, but I'm really excited to have my sister @jamielynnspears & @Tip on the record... #AskBritney
